# Main Concept
:CrisisResponseRequirement
    a owl:Class ;
    rdfs:isDefinedBy id:schema ;
    rdfs:subClassOf :Concept ;
    rdfs:label "Crisis response requirement"@en ;
    rdfs:comment "Any requirement related to crisis and emergency responses"@en ;
.


:CrisisResponseSkills
    a owl:Class ;
    rdfs:isDefinedBy id:schema ;
    rdfs:subClassOf :CrisisResponseRequirement ;
    rdfs:label "Crisis response skills"@en ;
    rdfs:comment "Any skills related to crisis and emergency responses"@en ;
.

